  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed development, by reason of its scale, design and siting, would be at odds with the design and layout of other units within Dickens Yard, to the detriment of the character and appearance of Dickens Yard. As such, the proposal would be contrary to Policies D3, D4, D8 and HC1 of the London Plan (2021) and Policies 7.4, 7B and 7C of the Ealing Development Management DPD (2013). | The proposed development, due to its siting near to a large, raised planter, and its proximity to a main residential entrance, would create a pinch point for pedestrians, disrupting the pedestrian circulation and flow through Dickens Yard, to the detriment of the public realm and amenity of Dickens Yard. As such, the proposal would be contrary to Policies D3, D4, D8 and HC1 of the London Plan (2021) and Policies 7.4, 7B and 7C of the Ealing Development Management DPD (2013)."
  ],
